					<ab>
						<title>Esther 7</title>
						<milestone unit="line" n="1"/>
						<l n="1" xml:id="Est-007-001"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבא</foreign>Da keldi ol bij da Haman ičḿa
							<milestone unit="line" n="2"/>Ester ol bijč́a byla.
						</l>
						<l n="2" xml:id="Est-007-002"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>Da ajtty ol bij Es-
							<milestone unit="line" n="3"/>terǵa daɣyn ol ekinči künd́a ičkisindía ol vinanyn
							<milestone unit="line" n="4"/>nedir kĺagij Ester e bijč́a da berilsin saja da nedir
							<milestone unit="line" n="5"/>qoltqaj senin jarty ol bijlikḱadejin da qylynsyn.
						</l>
						<l n="3" xml:id="Est-007-003"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותען
							</foreign><milestone unit="line" n="6"/>Da qaruv berdi Ester ol bijč́a da ajtty eger
							<milestone unit="line" n="7"/>taptym eśa širinlik közĺarijd́a e bij da eger
							<milestone unit="line" n="8"/>ol bijǵa jaḥšy körünśa berilsin maja ǯanym kĺagim-
							<milestone unit="line" n="9"/>d’a 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-007-add001" status="unremarkable"/>da
							<anchor xml:id="Est-007-add001" type="addSpan"/> ulusum qoltqamda.
						</l>
						<l n="4" xml:id="Est-007-004"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי</foreign>Ki satyldyq men da
							<milestone unit="line" n="10"/>ulusum tasetḿa qyrma da joq etḿa da eger
							<milestone unit="line" n="11"/>qullarɣa da qaravašlarɣa satylsajedik tyjylɣajedim ki ol
							<milestone unit="line" n="12"/>dušman tenši tüvüldu özüd́a izjanyna ol bijnin.
						</l>
						<milestone unit="line" n="13"/>
						<l n="5" xml:id="Est-007-005"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>Da ajtty ol bij Aḥašveroš da ajtty Es-
							<milestone unit="line" n="14"/>ter oj bijč́aǵa kimdi ol 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-007-add002" status="unremarkable"/>bu
							<anchor xml:id="Est-007-add002" type="addSpan"/> da qajsydy ol bu ki qunuš-
							<milestone unit="line" n="15"/>turdu any jüŕagi qylma alaj.
						</l>
						<l n="6" xml:id="Est-007-006"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">תיאמר</foreign>Da ajtty
							<milestone unit="line" n="16"/>Ester tar berüvčü kiši da dušman Haman ol jaman ošpu
							<milestone unit="line" n="17"/>da Haman alɣasandy 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-007-add003" status="unremarkable"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>lnynda
							<anchor xml:id="Est-007-add003" type="addSpan"/> bijnin da ol bijč́anin.
						</l>
						<l n="7" xml:id="Est-007-007"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והמלך
							</foreign><milestone unit="line" n="18"/>Da ol bij turdu qaḥiri byla ičkisind́an ol vinanyn ol
							<milestone unit="line" n="19"/>sarajdaɣy baɣɣa da Haman turdu qolma ǯany üčün Ester
							<milestone unit="line" n="20"/>ol bijč́ad́an ki kördü ki tüǵalč́a jetti anar ol jaman
							<milestone unit="line" n="21"/>ol bijd́an.
						</l>
						<l n="8" xml:id="Est-007-008"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והמלך</foreign>Da ol bij qajtty ol sarajdaɣy
							<milestone unit="page" n="382r"/><milestone unit="line" n="1"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">baɣ</supplied>dan üvüńa ičkisinin ol vinanyn da Haman tüš́are
							<supplied reason="lost">di</supplied>
							<milestone unit="line" n="2"/>ol krovat üstüńa ki Ester oltururedi anyn üs-
							<milestone unit="line" n="3"/>
							<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>üńa da ajtty ol bij daɣyn küč etḿamo 
							<addSpan spanTo="#Est-007-add004" status="unremarkable"/>o
							<supplied reason="lost">šol</supplied>
							<anchor xml:id="Est-007-add004" type="addSpan"/> ol bijjč́a-
							<milestone unit="line" n="4"/>ni kĺajsen qatymda üvd́a ol söz čyqty avzundan ol
							<milestone unit="line" n="5"/>bijnin da jüzĺari Hamannyn japtylar.
						</l>
						<l n="9" xml:id="Est-007-009"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>Da
							<milestone unit="line" n="6"/>ajtty Ḥarbona birisi ol vezirĺarnin alnynda ol
							<milestone unit="line" n="7"/>bijnin daɣyn muna ol aɣacta asqyc ünd́aĺadoɣan ki
							<milestone unit="line" n="8"/>qyldy Haman Mardeḫajɣa ki sözĺadi jaḥšyny ol bij üčün
							<milestone unit="line" n="9"/>turady üvünd́a Hamannyn bijikligi anyn enli lokot da
							<milestone unit="line" n="10"/>ajtty ol bij asajiz any anyn üstüńa.
						</l>
						<l n="10" xml:id="Est-007-010"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויתלו
							</foreign><milestone unit="line" n="11"/>Da astylar ošol Hamanny ol asqyč üstüńa ki
							<milestone unit="line" n="12"/>hadirl’aredi Mardeḫajɣa da ačuvu ol bijnin japryldy.
						</l>
					</ab>
